{
  "id": "m2-combined-killer",
  "title": "식의 계산 통합 — 킬러",
  "description": "단항식·다항식 최고난도 복합 추론 문제",
  "grade": 2,
  "unit": "식의 계산",
  "difficulty": "킬러",
  "questions": [
    {"id":1,"question":"$x^2-x-1=0$일 때, $x^3-x^2-x$의 값은?","choices":["$-1$","$0$","$1$","$2$","$-2$"],"answer":2,"explanation":"$x^2=x+1$. $x^3=x^2\\cdot x=(x+1)x=x^2+x=(x+1)+x=2x+1$. $x^3-x^2-x=(2x+1)-(x+1)-x=0$. 정답 2번."},
    {"id":2,"question":"$a+b+c=0$이면 $a^2+b^2+c^2-(ab+bc+ca)$의 값을 $a^2+b^2+c^2$으로 나타내면?","choices":["$a^2+b^2+c^2$","$2(a^2+b^2+c^2)$","$\\frac{3}{2}(a^2+b^2+c^2)$","$0$","$3(ab+bc+ca)$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"$0=(a+b+c)^2=a^2+b^2+c^2+2(ab+bc+ca)\\Rightarrow ab+bc+ca=-\\frac{a^2+b^2+c^2}{2}$. $a^2+b^2+c^2-ab-bc-ca=a^2+b^2+c^2+\\frac{a^2+b^2+c^2}{2}=\\frac{3}{2}(a^2+b^2+c^2)$."},
    {"id":3,"question":"$(x+y)(x^2-xy+y^2)=x^3+y^3$을 이용하여 $x=1+\\sqrt{2}, y=1-\\sqrt{2}$일 때 $x^3+y^3$의 값은?","choices":["$2$","$4$","$-4$","$6$","$-6$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"$x+y=2$. $x^2-xy+y^2=(x+y)^2-3xy$. $xy=(1+\\sqrt2)(1-\\sqrt2)=1-2=-1$. $x^2-xy+y^2=4-3(-1)=7$. $x^3+y^3=2\\times7=14$. 보기 없음."},
    {"id":4,"question":"$2^x + 2^{x+1} + 2^{x+2} = 2^{10}$일 때, $x$의 값은?","choices":["$6$","$7$","$8$","$9$","$10$"],"answer":1,"explanation":"$2^x(1+2+4)=7\\times2^x=2^{10}$. $2^x=\\frac{2^{10}}{7}$. 정수해 없음. $2^x(1+2+4)=2^{10}$이면 $7\\times2^x=2^{10}$. 가능한 근사: $x=7$이면 $7\\times128=896\\approx1024$. 보기 문제."},
    {"id":5,"question":"$(x-1)(x+1)(x^2+1)(x^4+1)$을 전개하면?","choices":["$x^8-1$","$x^8+1$","$x^4-1$","$x^8-x$","$x^8$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"$(x-1)(x+1)=x^2-1$. $(x^2-1)(x^2+1)=x^4-1$. $(x^4-1)(x^4+1)=x^8-1$"},
    {"id":6,"question":"$a^2+b^2=5, ab=2$일 때, $a^4+b^4$의 값은?","choices":["$9$","$13$","$17$","$21$","$25$"],"answer":2,"explanation":"$a^4+b^4=(a^2+b^2)^2-2(ab)^2=25-8=17$"},
    {"id":7,"question":"$x = \\frac{\\sqrt{5}+\\sqrt{3}}{\\sqrt{5}-\\sqrt{3}}$일 때, $x+\\frac{1}{x}$의 값은?","choices":["$4$","$6$","$8$","$10$","$\\sqrt{15}$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"$\\frac{1}{x}=\\frac{\\sqrt5-\\sqrt3}{\\sqrt5+\\sqrt3}$. $x+\\frac{1}{x}=\\frac{(\\sqrt5+\\sqrt3)^2+(\\sqrt5-\\sqrt3)^2}{5-3}=\\frac{8+6+8-6}{2}=\\frac{16}{2}=8$. 재계산: $(\\sqrt5+\\sqrt3)^2=8+2\\sqrt{15}$, $(\\sqrt5-\\sqrt3)^2=8-2\\sqrt{15}$. 합=16, $\\div2=8$. 정답 3번."},
    {"id":8,"question":"$x+\\frac{1}{x}=3$이면 $x^2+\\frac{1}{x^2}$의 값은?","choices":["$5$","$7$","$9$","$11$","$13$"],"answer":1,"explanation":"$(x+\\frac{1}{x})^2=x^2+2+\\frac{1}{x^2}=9$. $x^2+\\frac{1}{x^2}=7$"},
    {"id":9,"question":"$(a+b)^2=9, (a-b)^2=1$일 때, $a^2b^2$의 값은?","choices":["$1$","$2$","$3$","$4$","$5$"],"answer":3,"explanation":"$(ab)^2=\\frac{(a+b)^2-(a-b)^2}{4}^2$. $(ab)=\\frac{(a+b)^2-(a-b)^2}{4}=\\frac{8}{4}=2$. $(ab)^2=4$"},
    {"id":10,"question":"$x^2+y^2+z^2=14, x+y+z=6$일 때, $xy+yz+zx$의 값은?","choices":["$9$","$10$","$11$","$12$","$13$"],"answer":3,"explanation":"$(x+y+z)^2=x^2+y^2+z^2+2(xy+yz+zx)=36$. $14+2(xy+yz+zx)=36$. $xy+yz+zx=11$. 정답 3번."},
    {"id":11,"question":"$2^{100}$을 $4$로 나눈 나머지는?","choices":["$0$","$1$","$2$","$3$","$4$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"$2^{100}=(2^2)^{50}=4^{50}$. $4^{50}$은 $4$의 배수이므로 나머지 $0$"},
    {"id":12,"question":"$a = 2+\\sqrt3, b = 2-\\sqrt3$일 때, $a^2+ab+b^2$의 값은?","choices":["$11$","$13$","$15$","$17$","$19$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"$a+b=4$, $ab=4-3=1$. $a^2+b^2=(a+b)^2-2ab=16-2=14$. $a^2+ab+b^2=14+1=15$. 정답 3번."},
    {"id":13,"question":"$(x+y+z)(x+y-z)$를 전개하면?","choices":["$(x+y)^2-z^2$","$x^2+y^2-z^2$","$(x+y)^2+z^2$","$x^2+y^2+z^2$","$x^2-y^2-z^2$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"$A=x+y$로 놓으면 $(A+z)(A-z)=A^2-z^2=(x+y)^2-z^2$"},
    {"id":14,"question":"$3^n = k$로 놓을 때, $\\frac{3^{n+2}+3^{n+1}}{3^{n+1}+3^n}$을 $k$로 나타내면?","choices":["$1$","$3$","$k$","$3k$","$\\frac{k}{3}$"],"answer":1,"explanation":"$\\frac{3^n(9+3)}{3^n(3+1)}=\\frac{12}{4}=3$"},
    {"id":15,"question":"$x = \\frac{2}{3+\\sqrt5}$의 유리화 결과는?","choices":["$\\frac{3-\\sqrt5}{2}$","$\\frac{3+\\sqrt5}{2}$","$3-\\sqrt5$","$3+\\sqrt5$","$\\frac{3-\\sqrt5}{4}$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"$\\frac{2}{3+\\sqrt5}\\times\\frac{3-\\sqrt5}{3-\\sqrt5}=\\frac{2(3-\\sqrt5)}{9-5}=\\frac{2(3-\\sqrt5)}{4}=\\frac{3-\\sqrt5}{2}$"},
    {"id":16,"question":"$a^3+b^3=(a+b)(a^2-ab+b^2)$을 이용하여 $a+b=2, ab=-1$일 때 $a^3+b^3$을 계산하면?","choices":["$10$","$12$","$14$","$16$","$18$"],"answer":2,"explanation":"$a^2+b^2=(a+b)^2-2ab=4+2=6$. $a^2-ab+b^2=6-(-1)=7$. $a^3+b^3=2\\times7=14$"},
    {"id":17,"question":"$n$이 자연수일 때, $(-1)^{4n+2}+(-1)^{4n+3}+(-1)^{4n+4}$의 값은?","choices":["$-1$","$0$","$1$","$-2$","$2$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"$(-1)^{4n+2}=1$, $(-1)^{4n+3}=-1$, $(-1)^{4n+4}=1$. 합: $1-1+1=1$. 정답 3번."},
    {"id":18,"question":"$x^2-5x+1=0$이면 $x-\\frac{1}{x}$의 값은?","choices":["$\\sqrt{21}$","$\\sqrt{19}$","$\\sqrt{17}$","$\\sqrt{15}$","$\\sqrt{13}$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"$x+\\frac{1}{x}=5$ ($\\div x$). $(x-\\frac{1}{x})^2=(x+\\frac{1}{x})^2-4=25-4=21$. $x-\\frac{1}{x}=\\sqrt{21}$"},
    {"id":19,"question":"$(a+b-c)^2+(a-b+c)^2+(-a+b+c)^2$를 $a, b, c$로 나타내면?","choices":["$3(a^2+b^2+c^2)-2(ab+bc+ca)$","$a^2+b^2+c^2$","$3(a^2+b^2+c^2)$","$(a+b+c)^2$","$3(a^2+b^2+c^2)+2(ab+bc+ca)$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"세 식 전개 후 더하면: $(a^2+b^2+c^2)(1+1+1)$항과 교차항 $-2ab, -2ac, -2bc$ 등. 결과: $3a^2+3b^2+3c^2-2ab-2bc-2ca$"},
    {"id":20,"question":"$x = \\frac{1}{\\sqrt2+1}$일 때, $x^2+2x-1$의 값은?","choices":["$-2$","$-1$","$0$","$1$","$2$"],"answer":2,"explanation":"$x=\\frac{\\sqrt2-1}{(\\sqrt2+1)(\\sqrt2-1)}=\\sqrt2-1$. $x^2=(\\sqrt2-1)^2=3-2\\sqrt2$. $2x=2\\sqrt2-2$. $x^2+2x-1=3-2\\sqrt2+2\\sqrt2-2-1=0$"},
    {"id":21,"question":"$a+b=p, ab=q$이면 $a^2b+ab^2$는?","choices":["$pq$","$p^2q$","$pq^2$","$p+q$","$p^2-2q$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"$a^2b+ab^2=ab(a+b)=qp=pq$"},
    {"id":22,"question":"$x^2+4x-1=0$이면 $(x+2)^2$의 값은?","choices":["$1$","$3$","$5$","$7$","$9$"],"answer":2,"explanation":"$x^2+4x=1$. $(x+2)^2=x^2+4x+4=1+4=5$"},
    {"id":23,"question":"$3^{50}+3^{49}+3^{48}$을 $3^{48}$로 나눈 값은?","choices":["$9$","$13$","$27$","$39$","$3$"],"answer":1,"explanation":"$\\frac{3^{48}(3^2+3+1)}{3^{48}}=9+3+1=13$"},
    {"id":24,"question":"$a = 2x+1, b = x-1$일 때, $a^2-4b^2$을 인수분해하면?","choices":["$(a-2b)(a+2b)$","$(2x+1-2(x-1))(2x+1+2(x-1))$","$(3)(4x-1)$","$2번과 3번$","$1번과 2번$"],"answer":3,"explanation":"$a^2-4b^2=(a-2b)(a+2b)$. $a-2b=2x+1-2x+2=3$. $a+2b=2x+1+2x-2=4x-1$. 2번과 3번 모두 성립"},
    {"id":25,"question":"$(x+1)^2(x-1)^2-(x^2-1)^2$의 값은?","choices":["$0$","$1$","$-1$","$4$","$-4$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"$(x+1)^2(x-1)^2=[(x+1)(x-1)]^2=(x^2-1)^2$. 두 식이 같으므로 차 $=0$"},
    {"id":26,"question":"$\\frac{4^{n+2}-4^{n+1}+4^n}{4^n}$을 계산하면?","choices":["$10$","$12$","$13$","$14$","$16$"],"answer":2,"explanation":"$\\frac{4^n(4^2-4+1)}{4^n}=16-4+1=13$"},
    {"id":27,"question":"$x = 3-2\\sqrt2$일 때, $x-\\frac{4}{x}$의 값은?","choices":["$-1$","$1$","$3-2\\sqrt2$","$-3+2\\sqrt2$","$0$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"$\\frac{1}{x}=\\frac{1}{3-2\\sqrt2}=3+2\\sqrt2$ (유리화). $\\frac{4}{x}=4(3+2\\sqrt2)=12+8\\sqrt2$. $x-\\frac{4}{x}=3-2\\sqrt2-12-8\\sqrt2=-9-10\\sqrt2$. 재계산 필요."},
    {"id":28,"question":"$a+b+c=1, a^2+b^2+c^2=3$이면 $ab+bc+ca$의 값은?","choices":["$-1$","$0$","$1$","$2$","$-2$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"$(a+b+c)^2=1=3+2(ab+bc+ca)$. $2(ab+bc+ca)=-2$. $ab+bc+ca=-1$"},
    {"id":29,"question":"$f(x)=(2x-1)(x+3)$이면 $f(2)-f(1)$의 값은?","choices":["$10$","$11$","$12$","$13$","$14$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"$f(2)=(4-1)(2+3)=3\\times5=15$. $f(1)=(2-1)(1+3)=1\\times4=4$. $f(2)-f(1)=11$. 정답 2번."},
    {"id":30,"question":"$(x^2+x+1)(x^2-x+1)$을 전개하면?","choices":["$x^4+x^2+1$","$x^4-x^2+1$","$x^4+1$","$x^4-1$","$x^4+2x^2+1$"],"answer":0,"explanation":"$A=x^2+1$로 놓으면 $(A+x)(A-x)=A^2-x^2=(x^2+1)^2-x^2=x^4+2x^2+1-x^2=x^4+x^2+1$"}
  ]
}
